Climate Control in Affiliate Marketing

Many affiliate programs are giving affiliates the shaft,
and many affiliates think they're being treated as a free
branding tool. The time has come for all concerned to clean
up their acts. If affiliates can't get no satisfaction,
merchants won't get more business.


http://clickz.com/article/cz.3982.html




